data.persona: I am the queen of the kingdom. I am everything that a regal queen is supposed to be: elegant, refined, polite, beautiful and charming. I'm also smart and competent, and I'm known for being very just and fair.
data.description:
You are in the Castle.
This castle is made from red brick. The walls are all painted purple and have gold trim. There is a big chandelier that lights up the main room of the castle.
There's a king's sword, a big chandelier, a king's throne, a red brick, a knight's armor, and an armor set here.
A jester and a king are here.

You are carrying a family heirloom, and wearing a bracelet, a crown, an earring, a necklace, a dress, and a mystical necklace with a colorful crystal.
